This product is an independent TypeScript implementation of subgroup discovery
and exceptional model mining. Its semantics were developed against, and are
differentially tested against, the pysubgroup library, version 0.9.0
(https://github.com/flemmerich/pysubgroup), licensed under the Apache License
2.0, Copyright Florian Lemmerich and contributors. No pysubgroup source code
is included in this product beyond short attributed snippets documenting
semantic decisions (see COMPATIBILITY.md and docs/spec.md).

Academic users should cite:
  Lemmerich, F., & Becker, M. (2018). pysubgroup: Easy-to-Use Subgroup
  Discovery in Python. In ECML-PKDD 2018 (Demo Track).
